ng it can hold. Break down bigger card tasks into steps with file attachment previews, reminders, checklists and commentsemoji reactions included! Plus, gain powerful perspective by seeing all cards by list and status at the board level.Your team can:Manage deadlinesProvide and track feedbackAssign tasks and hand off workConnect work across appsnullMeet your new ButlerNo-code automationLet the robots do the workso your team can focus on work that matters. With Trellos built-in automation, Butler, reduce the number of tedious tasks (and clicks) on your project board by harnessing the power of automation across your entire team.Learn moreButler uses natural language commands to automate just about any task in Trello:Automate common actions like moving listsCreate custom buttons to build process quicklySurface upcoming deadlines to the teamSchedule teammate assignments, and more!nullPower-UpsIntegrate top work toolsEasily connect the apps your team already uses into your Trello workflow, or add a Power-Up that helps fine-tune one specific need. With hundreds of Power-Ups available, your teams workflow wishes are covered.Learn moreFrom Reporting to Custom Fields to your beloved software integrationsweve got functionalities, your favorites, and more!Such as:ConfluenceSlackDropboxGoogle DriveEvernotenullSee our pricingWhether youre a team of 2 or 2,000, theres a Trello tailor-made for your organization.Trello pricingnullTake a Trello tourExplore the world of boards and beyond in Trello. Dive deeper into our most popular features.Tour Trello eBay IndustryeCommercenullnullBharath Sundar Egencia IndustryTravelnullnullKerry Parker-Evans Detroit Red Wings IndustrySportnullnullHaydon Dotson Sprout Social IndustryMarketingnullnullHaley EnnesnullnullnullnullnullnullSign up and get started with Trello today. A world of productive teamwork awaits!nullSign upTrello also works great on your smaller screen.nullnull
